issue.title: It is impossible to specify the default value for the commentText property of a Radiogroup question type
issue.body:
Updated the following code should be used, since it is a localizable property:
```js
const engLocale = Survey.surveyLocalization.locales["en"];
engLocale.otherItemText = "New other text";
```
Here is [the example](https://codepen.io/andrew-telnov/pen/GRzpebL).

User Issue: T15266 - Add default value for Comment Area Text
https://surveyjs.answerdesk.io/internal/ticket/details/T15266
***
[View Demo](https://codesandbox.io/s/festive-james-czxz3j?file=/src/SurveyComponent.jsx)

The following code doesn't work:
```
import { Serializer } from "survey-core";

Serializer.findProperty("radiogroup", "commentText").defaultValue =
  "I want this to be default text";
```
![image](https://github.com/surveyjs/survey-library/assets/22372972/9d8ad627-2aaa-45a1-9fc9-25f72ebfe2af)

issue.title: Dynamic Matrix - No space between the last and total rows
issue.body:
With v1.9.104 and newer, no padding appear between the last row and the total row.
https://surveyjs.io/form-library/examples/questiontype-matrixdynamic-totals/reactjs

issue.title: File Question - An empty preview appears when the onDownloadFiles event returns with the options.callback('error')

labels.name: user issue
labels.description: An issue or bug reported by users

issue.body:
User Issue: T15217 - Add error message on the file preview
https://surveyjs.answerdesk.io/internal/ticket/details/T15217
***
Usage Scenario: a File Upload question allows uploading multiple files. However, certain file types are not allowed (exe). Therefore, the `onUploadFiles` function is implemented to upload only valid files. However, if a user tries to upload a single forbidden file, we return from the `onUploadFiles` function using the `options.callback('error')` function. In this case, an empty preview appears and all previously uploaded files disappear.

[View CodePen](https://codepen.io/JaneGaid/pen/zYevzqK)
![image](https://github.com/surveyjs/survey-library/assets/22372972/a3e543ea-1c32-4b12-a8ee-c827c23d1071)
